tched were so gallantly streaming? <br />\n在我們所看到的防禦土牆上是英勇地飄揚著<br />\n<br />\nAnd the rocket's red glare, the bombs bursting in air, <br />\n火箭的紅色火焰 以及在空中爆炸的炸彈<br />\n<br />\nGave proof through the night that our flag was still there:<br />\n證明了整個晚上我們的旗幟還在<br />\n<br />\nOh, say! does that star-spangled banner yet wave<br />\n噢 說吧 在自由的土地 以及勇者的<br />\n<br />\nO'er the land of the free and the home of the brave?<br />\n家園上星條旗猶飄揚乎(倒裝句)"},{"pid":"c74ed4146a1f374d3acae8ecc5f36e193430344f","tid":1714561,"uid":227789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:06:36.000Z","msg":"諗起孤星淚"},{"pid":"231ccbd030490f6c8fa8dbd8bd5a7b98395ea265","tid":1714561,"uid":177510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:12:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43e2693c65e7d3a87448621c96426c1de4bbc63d","tid":1714561,"uid":130693,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:15:09.000Z","msg":"將啲片配埋國歌rt出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d90ffd92f7f55dda1d2a7badd4a24bcab1c1299","tid":1714561,"uid":160348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:15:23.000Z","msg":"尋晚一路睇一路諗起美國國歌嘅情節，為咗保護旗幟不惜一切"},{"pid":"5843d3e507238357d140123d47077ed1c967142b","tid":1714561,"uid":197492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43e2693c65e7d3a87448621c96426c1de4bbc63d","tid":1714561,"uid":130693,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:15:09.000Z","msg":"將啲片配埋國歌rt出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:16:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"987594895eeb69e62295a5c7614ef7da74432761","tid":171